# OpenCode Scheduled Tasks
# 
# Format: minute hour day month weekday command
# All tasks run as the opencode user
#
# Examples:
#   0 23 * * *  - Daily at 11 PM
#   0 8 * * *   - Daily at 8 AM
#   */30 * * *  - Every 30 minutes
#   0 9 * * 1   - Weekly on Monday at 9 AM

# Nightly reflection and SOUL.md update (11 PM)
0 23 * * * /workspace/scripts/run-task.sh "Perform nightly reflection: Review today's activities from logs, reflect on what went well and what could improve, then update SOUL.md with insights, learned preferences, and any notable events. Be thoughtful and concise." reflection

# Example: Morning health check (8 AM) - uncomment to enable
# 0 8 * * * /workspace/scripts/run-task.sh "Morning check: Verify TrueNAS is healthy, check for any failed arr stack imports overnight, report summary." morning-check
